Name:         erlang
Summary:      erlang
Version:      19.1
Release:      1%{?dist}
Group:        Development/Languages
Vendor:       VMware, Inc.
Distribution: Photon
License:      ASL2.0
URL:          http://erlang.com
BuildArch:    x86_64
